            <description><![CDATA[
                            <h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Items are now moved to the closest position when changing their state</li>
                                <li>Adds update settings</li>
                                <li>When adding a new item, the list scrolls to the bottom to bring the new item into view</li>
                                <li>Adjusts the outline colour of the checkboxes</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Known Issues</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>When the list is not scrolled to the top, the burning animation may appear incorrectly</li>
                            </ul>
							]]></description>
